MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- provider_catalog: switch ollama from static_credential to
  credential_attr="ollama_api_key" — enables LiteLLM master key
  as Bearer auth when routing through the container stack
- settings: add OLLAMA_API_KEY field (default "ollama" for direct
  ollama, set to LITELLM_MASTER_KEY for stack mode)
- .env.example: strip to ollama-only, two-mode comments
  (Option A stack :4000 / Option B self-hosted :11434)
